Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.72,0:17:30.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位被强制监禁在此，我感到很抱歉\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Ladies and gentlemen, you're being detained against your will.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.89,0:17:35.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们无意伤害你们\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}For that, I apologize.It is not our intention in any way to harm you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.53,0:17:39.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只待我们的任务完成后，各位就会被立刻释放\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You will not be detained one minute longer than is necessary for us to complete our mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.27,0:17:47.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,立正\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Attention on deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.90,0:17:51.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位请稍息\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Stand easy, men.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.27,0:17:56.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别怀疑，我们正身处险境\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Make no mistake about it, gentlemen, we are now in harm's way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.55,0:17:59.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和巴克斯特少校\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}For Major Baxter and I,this is the last campaign in a career dating back...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.75,0:18:01.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在六八年越战就是同胞了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}to Tet '68.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.95,0:18:05.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同样的，亨德里克斯上尉和克里斯普中士\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Likewise for Captain Hendrix, Gunnery Sergeant Crisp,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.26,0:18:08.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟随我在波斯湾战争中开始了他们的军旅生涯\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}who cut their teeth under my command in Desert Storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.09,0:18:13.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而弗赖伊上尉和达罗上尉,这则是我首次与你们共事\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Captain Frye, Captain Darrow,this is my first operational situation with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.40,0:18:15.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们的表现的确名不虚传\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}And I have to say, thus far your conduct reflects your reputations.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.70,0:18:17.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-谢谢你，将军 -谢谢你，长官\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- Thank you, General. - Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.73,0:18:20.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们占领此地的的行动，沉着、准确又大胆\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}We have achieved our position through poise, precision and audacity.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.14,0:18:23.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为此，我们更要充满决心\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}To this we must now add resolve.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.47,0:18:26.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们会被视为叛国者\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}We'll be branded as traitors, the gravest capital crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.04,0:18:29.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最严重的罪犯最重可被判死刑\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Punishable by death.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.58,0:18:35.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,数百年前 华盛顿、杰斐逊、亚当斯等建国者\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Couple hundred years ago,a few guys named Washington,Jefferson and Adams...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.22,0:18:38.31,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也被英国视为叛国者\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}were branded as traitors by the British.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.49,0:18:41.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在他们则被视为爱国者\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}And now they're called patriots.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.52,0:18:43.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,历史将还我们清白\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}In time, so shall we.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.43,0:18:49.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如情况许可 凭着人质和VX毒气弹头\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}in less than 48 hours,we will  evacuate this island in gunships...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.57,0:18:52.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们将在48小时内撤离\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}under cover of hostages and V.X. gas warheads.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.07,0:18:56.51,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们的目的地是没有引渡条约国家\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Your destination: a non-extradition treaty country.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.74,0:19:00.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们每人将获得一百万美元的酬金\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You will each be paid a fee of $1 million for services rendered.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.01,0:19:05.47,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你们永远不能再踏上你们故乡的土地\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}But you can never again set foot on your native soil.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.65,0:19:09.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你们可以接受吗？ -可以，长官\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- Can you live with that? - Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.22,0:19:11.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海军陆战队侦搜大队\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}The men of Marine Force Recon are selected...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.06,0:19:16.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被派往世界各地执行非法任务\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}to carry out illegal operations throughout the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.26,0:19:18.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当他们战死异乡\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}When they don't come home...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.06,0:19:21.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,家人所得到的只有谎言\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}their families are told fairy tales about what happened to them...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.13,0:19:25.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有任何补偿\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}and denied compensation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.44,0:19:28.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些谎言我已忍受一辈子\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Well, I have choked on these lies my entire career!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.97,0:19:31.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在该在此停止这些谎言了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Well, here and now the lies stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.25,0:19:40.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上帝保佑你们，各就各位\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}God be with all of you. Man your positions, men.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.16,0:19:44.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,<font size=20 color=#00d8f8>华盛顿 七点四十分
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.12,0:19:47.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是联邦调查局局长沃马克\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}This is FBI Director Womack.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.42,0:19:50.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,局长，请听清楚\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Director, be advised.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.99,0:19:53.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有81名，我重复\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Eighty-one, I say again,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.93,0:19:57.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目前有81名人质在我手上\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}81 civilians are under my control as of this moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.87,0:20:02.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请将此列为最高机密\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You are to take measures to assure this remains a need-to-know classified fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.21,0:20:06.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你是谁？ -局长先生，你面临一个很严重的问题\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Who is this? Mr. Director, you have a very serious problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.51,0:20:09.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,VX毒气导弹如箭在弦\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}A battery of V.X. gas rockets is presently deployed to deliver...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.71,0:20:14.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,准备对旧金山湾区发出致命的一击\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}a highly lethal strike on the population of the San Francisco Bay area.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.52,0:20:16.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,午夜时我将再以电话通知，提出我的要求\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I will call again at 0100 hours to state my demands.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.52,0:20:19.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你是什么人？ -海军陆战队法兰斯・汉默准将\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}-I want to know who I'm talking to. -This is Brigadier General
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.19,0:20:23.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从恶魔岛发话，完毕\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Francis X. Hummel, United States Marine Corps, from Alcatraz,out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.69,0:20:27.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我马上取消你的约会\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I'll cancel your reservations.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.33,0:20:30.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,联络五角大厦,通知旧金山办公室\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Get the Pentagon. and call the San Francisco office.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.87,0:20:33.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来恶魔岛又重新开张了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}It seems Alcatraz was just reopened.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.97,0:20:37.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}<font size=20 color=#00d8f8>五角大楼 11点58分
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.97,0:20:37.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚汉默将军带领一群彪悍但无害的陆战队员\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Last night General Hummel, using brutal but nonlethal force...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.01,0:20:39.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在安全士官的眼前\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}under the guise of a security exercise,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.11,0:20:43.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,偷走十五枚VX毒气导弹\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}walked off with 15 V.X. poison gas rockets.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.31,0:20:45.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过程中他的一名手下丧生\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}He lost one of his own men in the process.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.38,0:20:49.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,汉默将军在越南的时候，他那时还是上校\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}That's General Hummel in Vietnam. I think he was a major at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.22,0:20:53.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在越南参与过三次任务 参与过巴拿马、格瑞那达和波斯湾战争\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Three tours in Vietnam, Panama, Grenada, Desert Storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.52,0:20:58.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,荣获三面紫星勋章，两面银星勋章,国会荣誉勋章\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Three Purple Hearts,two Silver Stars and the Congressional Medal of--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.43,0:21:01.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…天啊,这个人是个英雄\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Jesus! This man is a hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.96,0:21:04.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想“传奇英雄”应该是比较恰当的形容词\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Well, I think "legend" might be a better description, Mr. Sinclair.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.27,0:21:07.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们可在他的英雄事迹上加上绑架和勒索了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Well, now we can add kidnapping and extortion to his list of accolades.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.07,0:21:10.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辛克莱先生，汉默将军是条好汉\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Mr. Sinclair, General Hummel is a man of honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.77,0:21:13.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将军，是他\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}General, it's him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.71,0:21:19.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-法兰克，我是艾尔克・拉玛 -嗨…艾尔，你好吗？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}-Frank, it's AI Kramer. -Hi, Al, how you doin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.32,0:21:21.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不晓得，法兰克，你说呢？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I don't know, Frank. Ah, why don't you tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.05,0:21:24.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我这里有一堆忧虑的家伙，法兰克\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Got a lot of very, very worried people here, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.95,0:21:27.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就直说吧\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I'll come straight to the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.36,0:21:30.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我的指挥之下有83名陆战队员为国捐驱\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Eight-three Force Reconnaissance Marines have died under my various commands.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.59,0:21:32.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在寮国北部与中国南部牺牲了47名\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Forty-seven in northern Laos and southern China.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.96,0:21:36.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们从未承认曾派兵到中国南部去\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Southern China? We never admitted we sent troops into China.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.30,0:21:38.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是谁？表明身份\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Who is this? Identify yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.63,0:21:41.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白宫幕僚长海顿・辛克莱\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}White House Chief of Staff Hayden Sinclair, General.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.60,0:21:44.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你今年几岁？海顿・辛克莱幕僚长\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}How old are you, Chief of Staff Sinclair?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.14,0:21:47.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我33岁 -那么，辛克莱先生\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- I'm 33. - Well, Mr. Sinclair,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.78,0:21:50.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也许根本就不明白我在说什么\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}you've probably got no fucking idea what I'm talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.91,0:21:53.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你九岁时，我就在中国从事秘密活动\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}By your ninth birthday, I was runnin' black ops into China...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.42,0:21:56.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歼灭了两百名敌军\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}and my men were responsible f-for over 200 enemy kills.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.29,0:21:59.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿些胶带去帖住辛克莱先生的嘴\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Al, put some rigging tape over Mr.Sinclair's mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.32,0:22:02.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-他在浪费我的时间 -你想继续说吗，法兰克？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}-He's wasting my time. -Ah, you want to continue, Frank?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.83,0:22:04.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,记得波斯湾战争中\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Remember Operation Desert Storm?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.13,0:22:08.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,CNN播出的精准导弹攻击报导吗？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Those surgical hits made by our smart bombs, covered so well on CNN?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.00,0:22:13.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我在地面的手下用雷射瞄准目标而有此表现的\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}It was my men on the ground that made those hits possible by lasing the targets.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.77,0:22:17.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在战争之后，有二十人在巴格达壮烈牺牲\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Twenty of them were left to rot outside Baghdad after the conflict ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.27,0:22:21.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们的家人没有得到补偿，也没有获颁任何勋章\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}No benefits were paid to their families. No medals conferred.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.45,0:22:28.28,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们为国捐驱，却得不到军方的葬礼\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}These men died for their country, and they weren't even given a goddamn military burial.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.85,0:22:32.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,情况已让人忍无可忍\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}The situation is unacceptable.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.29,0:22:34.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们从红海贸易公司\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You will transfer $100 million from the Grand Cayman...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.99,0:22:37.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将一亿美元的金额转汇入我指定的帐户\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Red Sea Trading Company account to an account I designate.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.99,0:22:40.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这笔款项之中\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}From these funds, reparations of $1 million will be paid...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.00,0:22:43.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,83名军人遗属将会各得一百万元\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}to each of the 83 marines' families.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.50,0:22:46.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至于余款我则会妥善散发\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}The rest of the funds I will disperse at my discretion.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.14,0:22:49.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说得够清楚吗？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Do I make myself clear?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.41,0:22:52.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除了红海贸易公司，那是什么？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Except for the Red Sea Trading Company. What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.88,0:22:55.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-表明身份 -我是联邦调查局局长沃马克，将军\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- Identify yourself. - This is FBI Director Womack, General.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.88,0:22:59.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是五角大厦非法军售的地下基金\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}It's a slush fund where the Pentagon keeps proceeds from illegal arms sales.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.62,0:23:02.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托，法兰克，这是最高机密\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Jesus, Frank! This is classified information.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.22,0:23:05.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们若通知媒体，我就发射毒气导弹\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You alert the media, I launch the gas.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.69,0:23:08.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们若拒不付钱，我也会发射毒气导弹\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You refuse payment, I launch the gas.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.82,0:23:12.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们后天中午之前, 还有40小时可以安排把钱汇入\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You've got 40 hours, 'til noon day after tomorrow to arrange transfer of the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.96,0:23:16.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道反制措施, 你知、我也知，那一点也没用\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I am aware of your countermeasure. You know and I know it doesn't stand a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.90,0:23:18.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是汉默从恶魔岛发话，通话完毕\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Hummel from Alcatraz. Out.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.37,0:23:25.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们必须查明人质的身份，并个别通知他们的家属\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}We have to identify the hostages and contact each of their families.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.04,0:23:29.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要你们设法捏造理由，绝对不能泄密\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Uh, tell 'em somethin'. Make up a story, and we've got to keep this undercover.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.71,0:23:33.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,消息一旦泄露，旧金山将会一片混乱\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}If this comes out, the city of San Francisco will be in chaos. I am talking anarchy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.02,0:23:37.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等、等等\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Wait a minute, wait a minute. What is the potential casualty rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.59,0:23:42.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一枚VX毒气导弹潜在的杀伤力有多大？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}for a single rocket armed with V.X. poison gas, General Peterson?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.39,0:23:45.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-六至七吧 -那还好嘛\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- Sixty or seventy. - Well, that's, that's not so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.10,0:23:50.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,单位是万，有七万人会死亡\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Thousand. Seventy thousand dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.40,0:23:52.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一汤匙毒气掉到地上…\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- Oh. - One teaspoon of this hits the floor,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.14,0:23:55.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一百尺内的人畜皆亡\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}it's lethal up to a hundred feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.81,0:23:59.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一汤匙毒气在空中引爆…\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}One teaspoon of this shit detonated in the atmosphere...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.24,0:24:02.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八条街以内的生物将会无一幸免\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}will kill every living organism in an eight-block radius.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.58,0:24:05.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白了吗？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Get the point?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.21,0:24:07.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,汉默说的反制措施是指什么呢？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Uh, what did Hummel mean by your countermeasure, General?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.15,0:24:11.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,汽油燃烧弹能够把一般毒气烧光\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Standard poison is countered by napalm. It burns it up, consumes it upon detonation.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.85,0:24:15.81,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但VX毒气导弹的设计却是能抵抗汽油燃烧弹\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Now, the problem with V.X. poison gas is that it's designed specifically...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.03,0:24:19.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 因此才会发展铝热剂 - 将军，请您继续\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}to withstand napalm.That's where thermite plasma comes in. General Peterson?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.40,0:24:22.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,铝热剂燃烧弹的热度够高，足以消耗VX毒气\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}-General Peterson? -Thermite plasma incendiary systems....
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.83,0:24:25.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是还在测试之中\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}can burn hot enough to consume V.X. but they're still in the test phase;
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.04,0:24:29.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还不能上线使用,汉默一清二楚\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}it's not operational. Hummel knows this.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.94,0:24:32.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们在跟一个聪明的混蛋打交道呢\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}We are dealing with one smart son of a bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.14,0:24:35.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在36小时内\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}What's it gonna take to equip a flight of F-18s...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.85,0:24:38.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能不能把铝热剂准备好？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}with thermite plasma... within the next 36 hours?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.55,0:24:41.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-只有靠上帝了 -你说什么？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- An act of God. - Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.08,0:24:44.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们尽力而为\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}All right, we can try.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.55,0:24:48.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过我建议将此列为辅助对策\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}But I strongly urge you to consider the use of this as a secondary initiative.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.56,0:24:50.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我们必须采取主要对策了，上将\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Then we have to go to our primary initiative. Uh, Admiral?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.06,0:24:54.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要请特遣队队长安德森来参与行动\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Sir, I'd like to bring in our SEAL ground commander, Commander Anderson.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.70,0:24:59.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沃马克先生，你们局里最顶尖的生化专家是谁？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Mr. Womack, who is your best chemical/biological man?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.74,0:25:01.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有意思\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Oh, that's interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.00,0:25:04.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很吸引人\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- Oh, yeah. - That's very compelling.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.68,0:25:10.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢我的辫子吗？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You like my pigtails?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.31,0:25:13.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的辫子很俏皮\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Oh, yeah, the pigtails are very naughty.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.42,0:25:16.28,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很性感\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Naughty. Naughty.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.45,0:25:19.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,意大利奶油和桃红点心\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Just the Amaretto cream with peach sorbet persuasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.29,0:25:22.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}This isn't happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.22,0:25:24.45,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别接电话 不会这样吧\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- No, Stan, don't answer it. - This isn't happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.63,0:25:27.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别去接\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- No, just don't answer it. It's okay. - I have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.23,0:25:29.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一定得接，他们知道我在家\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- I have to. It's the office,baby. They know I'm home. - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.53,0:25:33.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-他们怎么会知道你在家呢 -他们是联邦调查局\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- How could they possibly know that you're home? - It's the FBI.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.31,0:25:39.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-史丹利… -我是古斯比\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}-Stanley! -Goodspeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.58,0:25:42.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对…好吧，我十分钟后就下楼\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Uh, yeah. O-Okay, yeah. I'll be, I'll be down,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.38,0:25:45.31,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- downstairs in ten minutes. - No, you won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.52,0:25:51.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我得去旧金山 -不，你不能去\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- I have to go to San Francisco. - No, you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.12,0:25:55.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,史丹利，你不必去旧金山\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Stanley, no, you do not have to go to San Francisco.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.52,0:25:58.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你现在在跟我开玩笑吗？ -你必须要留下来，我们有些事要谈清楚\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Are you kidding me right now? You need to stay here and talk to me about things.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.36,0:26:01.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我得走了，宝贝 -我可是天主教徒\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}-I've got to go, baby. -Oh! I am Catholic!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.56,0:26:03.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你明白这一点吗？我未婚怀孕\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Do you realize that? I am pregnant and I am unmarried.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.00,0:26:06.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这对我来说问题可大了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}And this causes a serious problem for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.50,0:26:08.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真不能相信你\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I cannot believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.55,0:26:19.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.68,0:26:23.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我爱你\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.32,0:26:27.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会娶你,我只是没有预期你会怀孕\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I will marry you. I just didn't plan on this, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.82,0:26:30.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也来旧金山吧\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Come to San Francisco.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.86,0:26:33.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-真的吗？ -是啊，我相信这只是例行训练\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- Really? - Yeah, I'm sure it's just a training exercise.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.03,0:26:36.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们住旅馆，点些香槟喝\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Check into the hotel. Order up some champagne.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.43,0:26:38.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 继续我们的游戏 - 没错\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- And we'll finish what we started? - Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.67,0:26:40.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你会娶我吗？ - 当然\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- Baby, you're gonna marry me? - You know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.94,0:26:44.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要娶我？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You're gonna marry me! Oh, honey, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.61,0:26:46.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 亲爱的，很快就好了 - 噢…我得走了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- Just a really quick one. - Oh, oh, I gotta go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.21,0:26:50.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,月圆之夜在夜间空降偷袭是行不通的\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}A nighttime airdrop incursion is out due to the full moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.28,0:26:52.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同样的，抢滩攻击也不行\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Likewise a frontal seaside attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.52,0:26:55.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我们被汉默发现，他会发射导弹的\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}If we're compromised and shots are fired, Hummel might launch.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.55,0:26:58.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唯一可行的方法，是从监狱内部攻击\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Our only alternative is an attack from within the prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.35,0:27:01.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们从监狱底部的隧道潜入中央地区\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}We penetrate the island through the tunnels under the prison buildings undetected...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.92,0:27:05.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那样我们就能由后方突击那些陆战队员\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}and emerge in its center; that way we can jump the marines from behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.23,0:27:08.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我们幸运的话 也许不必开枪就能够夺回导弹\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}And if we're lucky, take their rocket positions without a shot fired.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.83,0:27:11.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道，你研究过建筑蓝图吗？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I don't understand. You-you've studied the architectural plans?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.60,0:27:15.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有用，恶魔岛重新翻修过多次\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}They're useless. Alcatraz has been ripped up and rebuilt for years.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.44,0:27:18.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-地底下就像迷宫 -毫无疑问的\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- Under there is a maze of shit. - Well, there's no question, gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.57,0:27:20.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们需要熟悉那些地道的专家\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}We need firsthand intelligence of the tunnel systems.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.11,0:27:24.31,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-前任典狱长呢？ -一九七九年就死了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- So what about the former warden? - Died in 1979.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.45,0:27:26.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们联络过其他的狱警，都没有用\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}All the guards we contacted were useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.88,0:27:31.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道有人帮的上忙\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Um, there is someone who I think can help us.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.06,0:27:36.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是为了国家安全\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}This is for the sake of national security.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.06,0:27:41.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是为了国家安全，33年前才会这样做\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}No!It's the sake of national security that got us here in the first place 33 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.53,0:27:44.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道有一天我们会被反噬，想都别想！\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I knew! I knew someday this would come back to bite us.Forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.00,0:27:47.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 他不存在 - 他的确存在！\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- He does not exist. - He does exist!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.24,0:27:51.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三十年来我们只是选择把他忘掉 我们把他关起来，然后让他永不见天日\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}He does exist! We just chose to forget him for 30 years. We locked him up and threw away the key.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.87,0:27:53.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他可给我们惹了不少麻烦\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Oh, and a lot of goddamn good it did us.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.08,0:27:57.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他曾从两座高安全措施的监狱逃出来过 如果被他逃到街上…\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}He broke out of two maximum-security prisons. And if he hits the streets--
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.41,0:27:59.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他不会逃到街上的\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}He's not gonna hit the streets, Jim.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.82,0:28:02.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三十年前, 他是皇家特种部队的顶尖情报员\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Thirty years ago he was a highly-trained SAS operative.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.92,0:28:07.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他现在已跟我一样老了 我每晚还得爬起来上三次厕所呢\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}He is my age now,for Christ's sake! I have to get up three times a night to take a piss.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.79,0:28:10.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们不能冒险放他出来\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}We can't risk letting him out.
