Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.05,0:30:19.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是欧内斯特・帕克斯顿，联邦调查局西岸负责人\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}This is Ernest Paxton, agent in charge of the West Coast operation.
