Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.12,0:30:24.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幸会，先生 - 今天真是耐人寻味\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- How do you do, sir? - It's been a fairly interesting day so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.76,0:30:26.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,犯人已经在这里了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}The prisoner's here. Shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.10,0:30:30.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的属下找不到他的档案\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Now, my boys, they haven't been able to find a file on this guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.63,0:30:33.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-他到底是谁，长官？ -他叫约翰・梅森\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- Who is he anyway, sir? - His name is John Mason,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.37,0:30:37.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是一名英国人，一九六二年被关进恶魔岛\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}a British national incarcerated on Alcatraz in 1962,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.34,0:30:39.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一九六三年逃狱\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}escaped in '63.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.88,0:30:44.31,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我以为没人逃出过恶魔岛呢 -帕克斯顿，别跟我争辩\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- I was under the impression that no one ever escaped Alcatraz, sir. - Paxton, don't argue!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.48,0:30:48.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个人在美国和英国都没有身份\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}This man has no identity, not in the United States or Great Britain.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.75,0:30:51.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他不存在，懂吗？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}He does not exist. Understand? I want one thing:
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.09,0:30:55.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只要知道，他是怎么逃出恶魔岛的 特别是他逃亡的路径\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}how he escaped The Rock.Specifically, the route he took through the island's bowels.
