Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.36,0:31:04.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有…帕克斯顿 别对梅森来硬的，我太了解他了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}And Paxton, no strong-arming Mason. I know him too well.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.93,0:31:07.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你了解他，为何你不亲自去问他呢？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Well, if you know him, then why don't you question him?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.80,0:31:11.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他记得我,我不希望他的愤怒搞砸整件事\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}No, he'll remember me. I don't want his anger clouding the issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.81,0:31:13.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我搞定他吧\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}All right, I'll take care of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.98,0:31:25.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅森先生，我是负责人，欧内斯特・帕克斯顿\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Mr. Mason, I'm Special Agent in Charge, Ernest Paxton.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.99,0:31:30.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,负责什么？负责再多关我三十年？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}In charge of what? Fucking me over for another three decades?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.83,0:31:33.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不晓得你的过去, 我之所以来此是因为\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I don't know anything about your previous matters. I'm here because...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.93,0:31:37.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们面临一个特别的状况，我们认为你可能帮得上忙\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}a special situation exists that we feel you might be able to help us with.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.63,0:31:41.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那会是什么事？ 我被关得还比尼尔森・曼德拉还久\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Now,what might that be?I've been in jail longer than Nelson Mandela,
