Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.71,0:31:46.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-不是 -可惜\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- Not exactly. - Mmm, a pity.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.91,0:31:50.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好比阿尔卡姆内斯\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- I feel rather like Alcamenes. - Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.25,0:31:53.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔卡姆内斯，在古希腊时代被国王所囚禁\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Alcamenes. He was imprisoned by his king in ancient Greece.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.72,0:31:56.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沃尔特・雷利爵士也一样 拥有相同遭遇\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Like Sir Walter Raleigh. The same fate.
