Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.82,0:32:03.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该知道历史会重演\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}must be aware that, uh,there's a certain pattern emerging here.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.16,0:32:07.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-还有亚历山大・索尔仁尼琴 -我知道\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- Aleksandr Solzhenitsyn? - Yeah, I heard of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.13,0:32:10.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是帮共产党摇旗呐喊的家伙\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Didn't he play hockey for the fuckin' Red Wings?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.70,0:32:13.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-就是他 -我们干脆明讲吧，老兄\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- That's the chap. - Get this straight, pops.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.30,0:32:15.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们互不欣赏\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I don't like you any more than you like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.74,0:32:18.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我来此是要向你提出合理的条件\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}But I'm here to make you a legitimate offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.24,0:32:20.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到底想不想听？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You wanna hear what I have to say or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.54,0:32:24.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尽管说吧，亲爱的帕克斯顿\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}By all means, dear Paxton. By all means.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.41,0:32:27.51,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们在一个你所熟悉的地方遇到了麻烦\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}We got a problem in a place that I think you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.68,0:32:30.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恶魔岛上有人质危机\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}There's a hostage situation on Alcatraz.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.42,0:32:34.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-人质？ -81名观光客\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- Hostage? - Eighty-one tourists.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.22,0:32:37.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恶魔岛变成观光胜地？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}The Rock has become a tourist attraction?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.43,0:32:41.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,废话少说 你对恶魔岛t如指掌，你从那里逃过狱\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Why don't we cut the shit, huh? You know The Rock.You broke out.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.30,0:32:44.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对，我成功了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- Yes, successfully. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.80,0:32:47.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要你肯帮我们这个忙\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}So why don't you do yourself a favor while you're helpin' us?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.34,0:32:50.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趁还活着赶快出狱多好\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I mean, it'd be nice to get out of jail while you're still vertical.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.31,0:32:53.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趁你那话儿还有用的时候\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Hmm? While you got a little lead left in your pencil.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.14,0:32:57.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我考虑你的条件的期间\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}While I'm considering your offer...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.05,0:33:02.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要住进费尔蒙酒店的套房\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I want a suite in the Fairmont Hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.32,0:33:05.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是来这里谈条件的\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You know I'm here to cut you a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.29,0:33:09.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可不是来被你耍着玩的\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I am not here to bend over and take it up the ass from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.73,0:33:12.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来，我给你个铜板\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Here. Here's a quarter.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.43,0:33:20.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帮你自己一个忙吧, 打电话通知你的律师\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Do yourself a favor. Call your lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.27,0:33:22.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你得回到牢里\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You're goin' back to jail.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.04,0:33:28.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你要把他送回监狱？ -我哪里都不送他去\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- Y-You're sending him back to jail? - I'm not sending him anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.34,0:33:31.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是要让他好好想想\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I'm just givin' him somethin' to think about.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.75,0:33:33.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们没时间让他坐下来仔细的想\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I don't think we have time for him to just sit around and think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.98,0:33:37.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？ -对，古斯比说的对,你去和他谈\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- Oh, really? - No, Goodspeed's right. You go talk to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.09,0:33:40.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我？ - 对！ -长官，我还不够资格呢\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- Me?Sir, I'm not qualified for that. - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.92,0:33:44.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你是FBI探员 -你的专长是什么来着？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- You're an FBI agent! - W-What is your specialty again?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.26,0:33:46.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 化学武器 - 这点提都别提\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- Chemical weapons. - Don't mention that!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.80,0:33:53.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你要我说谎？ -没错，说谎\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- You want me to lie? - Yeah, lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.80,0:33:57.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们剩不到二十四小时了，你就试试看吧\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}We got less than 24 hours. Give it a shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.68,0:34:01.51,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.68,0:34:07.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨！\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.02,0:34:10.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是…\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I'm an agent with the, uh,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.89,0:34:13.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,联邦…FBI的人\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}uh, F-Federal--FBI
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.62,0:34:17.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫史丹利・古斯比\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- Eh, well, my-- I'm Stanley Goodspeed.
