Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.73,0:34:26.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我当然是 -你们有紧急状况\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- Of course I am. Huh. - And you have an emergency.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.37,0:34:29.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 是的\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.84,0:34:34.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你们需要我帮忙 -一点也没错\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- And you need my help. - Exactly right.
