Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.10,0:53:16.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-真的？ -没错，小姐\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- He is? - Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.36,0:53:19.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,约翰，我想我们该走了吧\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Well, gee whiz, John, I guess we oughta get goin', huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.80,0:53:23.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,随你吩咐，史丹利\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Whatever you say, Stanley.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.38,0:53:30.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你，你大可不必那样做的\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Thank you for that. You could've handled it differently.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.78,0:53:34.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们废话少说吧，混球\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}What do you say we cut the chitchat, a-hole?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.22,0:53:38.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,差点害死我两次，我的下巴痛死了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You almost got me killed twice. And my jaw hurts like hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.35,0:53:41.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-很好 -卑鄙的家伙！\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- Good. - Cocksucker!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.26,0:53:44.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我应该把你送回大牢\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}If I had my way, you would be shipped back to Wolfburg in leg irons...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.79,0:53:47.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让你的余生永远不见天日\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}and caged like an animal for the rest of your natural fucking life!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.33,0:53:49.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你毁了半个旧金山\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You wrecked half the city!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.03,0:53:56.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请你说明地下隧道\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- Give me a hand with the system. - Now, tell me about the tunnels.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.67,0:54:00.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要摸熟整个系统，你哪儿都能去\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}If you know the system, it will take you wherever you need to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.51,0:54:05.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里有个水管入口，它低于水面 那是我们最佳的入口吗？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}There's an intake pipe here, below low tide. Is that our best access?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.15,0:54:09.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对，我就是从这儿逃出\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- Yes. That's exactly where I had come out. - Then beneath the cistern,,,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.58,0:54:11.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,贮水池底下连结着污水处理系统\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}there's a connection to the abandoned septic system.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.12,0:54:16.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-那有多长？ -嗯…57步\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- How many feet is that? - Ehh... 57 paces.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.09,0:54:19.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后要怎么走？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Where do we go from there?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.87,0:54:27.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,问得好\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}That's a good question.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.20,0:54:32.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我不晓得 -什么？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- I have no idea. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.81,0:54:36.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是说，进去了我才知道\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I mean, I'll know it when we're all inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.18,0:54:39.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不能去，用蓝图跟我们解释\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}No. You're not goddamn goin'. Show us on the blueprints.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.85,0:54:43.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行，我的蓝图在我脑里\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I can't! My blueprint was in my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.35,0:54:46.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我曾经在黑暗中潜伏在地底三天\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I was underground for three days in the dark...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.89,0:54:49.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等待正确的潮汐到来\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}just waiting for the tides to be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.19,0:54:52.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别担心，我会记起来的\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}But don't worry. It'll all come back to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.46,0:54:55.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你哪儿都别想去，梅森\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You're not going anywhere, Mason.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.73,0:54:57.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.33,0:55:01.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他可能是他们唯一的希望\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Now, this piece of work might be the only chance those people over there have.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.84,0:55:04.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果他不去，那我们放他出来干嘛？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}If he's not going, then why the hell did we get him out of jail?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.71,0:55:07.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 他很聪明 - 他只能指路，不能跟去\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- He's smart. - I got him out to get you people in, not go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.01,0:55:11.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果他是唯一清楚的人，他就得去了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}If it's the only way of getting the intelligence I need, then he goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.05,0:55:13.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他会害你们\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}He'll fuck with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.08,0:55:17.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你若敢害我兄弟，我会让你死的很惨\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You compromise my men's lives, and I'll bury you out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.72,0:55:24.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沃马克，我看你别无选择了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Now, Womack...you're between The Rock and a hard case.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.99,0:55:28.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的手没事吧？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}How is your bowling arm?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.83,0:55:33.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,古斯比博士, 目标是要摧毁发射架\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Dr. Goodspeed, the goal is to take out the launchers,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.10,0:55:36.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,并且拆除VX毒气弹\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}then neutralize the V.X. chemical rounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.37,0:55:38.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们从卫星感热图看出，导弹在停尸间\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Well, we know the poison's being kept in the prison morgue...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.07,0:55:42.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是这里，颜色变深的地方\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}from the satellite thermal imaging, which is right here-- these colorized dots.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.61,0:55:44.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看过真正的毒气导弹吗？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Have you ever actually seen one of these devices?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.81,0:55:46.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，我只研究过\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}No, sir, but I've studied them.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.91,0:55:50.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我该开始教你们如何拆除导弹引信并解毒\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I should really begin briefing your guys on defusing and detoxification.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.52,0:55:53.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我这里有张图，是毒胶囊和导弹的结构详图\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Got a really neat layout over here of the chem round as well as the rocket...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.52,0:55:56.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我们就开始吧 -没有必要\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- so let's get rolling. - That won't be necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.96,0:56:00.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常有必要\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Oh, it's very necessary, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.73,0:56:03.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种毒气的杀伤力惊人\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}The power of this chemical is way beyond anything you can imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.73,0:56:06.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会造成生态浩劫的\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}An ecological disaster, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.53,0:56:08.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再加上它的设计相当复杂\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Plus the devices themselves are complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.04,0:56:11.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以你得跟来\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}That's why you're coming with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.01,0:56:15.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.31,0:56:18.47,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是专家，有问题吗？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You're the expert. What's your problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.65,0:56:22.81,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得跟去？一起潜到水底？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You mean I'm going, going out there, under the water?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.98,0:56:27.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你今天早上不是要枪吗？ 你现在有枪和潜水衣了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Well, earlier today you wanted a gun. Now you're getting a gun and a wet suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.06,0:56:29.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你参加过战斗吗？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Have you ever been in a combat situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.19,0:56:33.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-请解释战斗的定义 -薜普\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- Define "combat," sir. - Shep?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.46,0:56:36.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通过水下潜入,袭击在强固碉堡内的海陆精英\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}An incursion underwater to retake an impregnable fortress...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.46,0:56:39.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,救出81名被强行扣押的人质\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}held by an elite team of U.S. Marines in possession of 81 hostages...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.30,0:56:42.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夺回十五枚装有VX毒气的导弹\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}and 15 guided rockets armed with V.X. poisoned gas.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.04,0:56:47.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来，我没有参加过，失陪一下\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Oh. In that case, no, sir. Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.71,0:56:56.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- Here. - Ah, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.49,0:57:00.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你脸色不太好\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You don't look too good.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.99,0:57:03.51,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事实上简直是糟透了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}In fact, you look like shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.72,0:57:07.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的肚子在天翻地复\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}My stomach's doing hula hoops around my ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.00,0:57:11.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧？ 我是说，你办得到吗？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You all right?I mean, you gonna make it through this thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.90,0:57:14.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.30,0:57:17.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道一定会面对这种事\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I always expected something like this was going to happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.44,0:57:19.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么准备都没用的\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}but nothing prepares you for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:19.61,0:57:22.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在整个城市的命运\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Now I'm-- I'm responsible...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.91,0:57:25.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都系在我的手中\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}for a whole city.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.71,0:57:29.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道这对你而言并不简单\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Look,I Know this isn't easy for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.72,0:57:32.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你受过这方面的训练\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Remember, you were trained for this kind of a situation...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.19,0:57:34.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你会想得起来的\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}and believe me, it'll come back to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.19,0:57:36.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更何况还有全国最顶尖的特遣队会帮你\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Besides, you got the best SEAL team in the country backing you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.96,0:57:40.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧，你说得对\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Okay. You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.73,0:57:44.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会在无线电上指点你\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I-I'll be on the wire. I'll help talk you through it.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.90,0:57:49.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-还有一件事 -很糟糕\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}There's something else. It's terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.40,0:57:53.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，很美好...现在却很糟糕\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}N-No, it's wonderful... except it isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.47,0:57:57.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我女友怀孕了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}My girlfriend's pregnant...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.28,0:58:01.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她正飞来旧金山看我\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}and she's just flown in to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.62,0:58:04.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你今晚尽管专心完成任务\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You keep your mind on what you're going to be doing out there tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.45,0:58:08.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会派人把你女友接到指挥中心来的\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}And I'll send someone to pick up your girlfriend and bring her here to the command center.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.20,0:58:24.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-汉默 -哈，法兰克，我是林斯壮\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Hummel! - Hello, Frank. Lou Linstrom.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.17,0:58:27.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克拉玛将军和我正在白宫\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I'm at the White House with General Kramer.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.04,0:58:31.81,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,法兰克，我们在转帐时出了点问题\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Uh, Frank, uh, we're havin' a few problems with the account transfer.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.95,0:58:34.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别唆，我要解决方法\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Don't tell me problems. Tell me solutions.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:34.35,0:58:38.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们跟总统谈过 你知道总统对恐怖行动的立场\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Now, We've spoken to the president. and I know that you're aware of his stance on terrorism.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:38.79,0:58:42.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-所以我们打算… -这不是恐怖行动,这是关于正义\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- So what we'd like to do is-- - This isn't about terrorism. This is about justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.12,0:58:45.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也是要提醒你那些你为政治理由而遗弃的人\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}It's about reminding you people who found it politically convenient to forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.09,0:58:49.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-这样说是没用的，法兰克 -让我告诉你吧\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- This is goin' nowhere, Frank. - Well, then, let me tell you what is.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.20,0:58:52.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十五枚毒气弹将会击中旧金山市中心\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Fifteen V.X. gas rockets into the heart of San Francisco.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.07,0:58:55.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我给你十七小时去弄钱\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You've got 17 hours to deliver the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.37,0:58:57.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,否则后果将不堪设想，各位\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Or be prepared to reap the whirlwind, gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.11,0:59:04.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,铝热剂好了吗？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}What's the word from Mojave?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.41,0:59:09.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,彼得森将军不能保证能够起作用\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}General Peterson can give us no definite assurance on the thermite plasma.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.25,0:59:11.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就这样了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}That is the word.
