Dialogue: 0,1:10:08.61,1:10:11.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,折射回原点\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}send the beam back to its source...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:11.81,1:10:13.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后我就移开棱镜\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}and then I'm gonna move the prism.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:18.28,1:10:20.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,澡堂的震动感应器有动静，长官\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}We've got motion on a trembler in the shower room, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:20.89,1:10:22.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我们有访客了 -走吧\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}We've got visitors. Let's move.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:25.99,1:10:28.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了，可以出去\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Got it. Good to go.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:34.03,1:10:36.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,留下来，我们先清场\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Stand fast. We'll secure the area.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:47.18,1:10:50.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们进入澡堂了，长官\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}They're entering into the shower room, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.19,1:10:55.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们正在清场\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}They're securing the area.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:04.10,1:11:06.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别乱动\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Just sit tight.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:08.70,1:11:12.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放下武器！\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Drop your weapons! Drop 'em!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:12.71,1:11:14.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-放下武器，快点 -别开枪！\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- Stand fast! - Hold your fire!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:14.97,1:11:16.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-放下武器 -别开枪！\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- Drop your weapons! - Hold your fire!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:19.95,1:11:21.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是个他妈的陷阱\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}It's a fucking trap.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:23.68,1:11:27.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是汉默准将，放下武器\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}This is General Hummel. Drop your weapons.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:27.39,1:11:29.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放下来\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Drop 'em!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:29.22,1:11:34.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是安德森中校，汉默将军 特遣队队长\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Anderson here, General Hummel. Commander. Team leader.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:34.99,1:11:37.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安德森中校，如果你爱惜兄弟性命\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Commander Anderson,  if you have any concern for the lives of your men...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:38.10,1:11:41.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就命令他们放下武器\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}you will order them to safety their weapons and place them on the deck.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:41.27,1:11:42.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}This is not happening.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:42.74,1:11:48.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们知道你的目的 我也完全同意你\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Sir, we know why you're out here. God knows I agree with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:48.24,1:11:52.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我也跟你一样，誓言捍卫祖国抵挡敌人\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}But like you, I swore to defend this country against all enemies...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:52.51,1:11:56.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不论他们是外国人或是本国人\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}foreign, sir, and domestic.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:56.72,1:12:01.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将军，我们都为这国家洒下热血\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}General, we've spilled the same blood in the same mud.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:01.25,1:12:04.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我不能下达这个命令\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You know goddamn well I can't give that order.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:04.26,1:12:05.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们死定了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}We're dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:05.93,1:12:09.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们居高临下，中校\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Your unit is covered from an elevated position, Commander.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:09.46,1:12:13.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会再要求你了 别做傻事\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I'm not gonna ask you again. Don't do anything stupid.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:13.30,1:12:15.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有人愿意死在这里\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}No one has to die here.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.84,1:12:20.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟着将军的这些人 你们在海军陆战队誓言效忠国家\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Men following the general, you're under oath as United States Marines!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:20.31,1:12:22.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们忘了吗？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Have you forgotten that?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:23.44,1:12:25.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们都有袍泽丧命战场\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}We all have shipmates we remember.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:25.68,1:12:28.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有些甚至是被五角大厦的人所遗弃\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Some of them were shit on and pissed on by the Pentagon.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:29.12,1:12:32.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你们也无权叛变啊！\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}But that doesn't give you the right to mutiny!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.42,1:12:35.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,随你怎么说，我们占了优势\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You call it what you want! You're down there, we're up here.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:35.29,1:12:37.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你们犯了大错，中校 - 别动\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You walked into the wrong goddamn room, Commander!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:37.29,1:12:39.28,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该死，中校，最后一次\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- Stand fast! - Goddamn it, Commander, one last time.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:39.46,1:12:41.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,命令你的手下放下武器\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You tell your men to safety their weapons, drop 'em on the deck.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:41.49,1:12:44.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我无法下达那个命令 - 我不想再说一次\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- I cannot give that order! - I am not gonna repeat that order!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:44.36,1:12:47.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我无法下达那个命令 - 你是怎么了？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- I will not give that order! - What the hell is wrong with you, man?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:47.33,1:12:49.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别动！别动…\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- Stand fast! - Oh, my God!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:49.97,1:12:51.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我再说一次… - 哦！天哪！干掉他们吧\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- Let's waste these fuckers. - One last time.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:01.25,1:13:03.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停火！\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Cease fire!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:26.84,1:13:28.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停火！\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Cease fire!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:37.65,1:13:39.45,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停火！\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Cease fire!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:39.62,1:13:43.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该死、可恶！放开我,放开我\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Shit, Goddamn it Let go of me,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:43.99,1:13:46.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别去\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Don't,don't go.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:24.06,1:14:25.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Fuck
Dialogue: 0,1:14:35.74,1:14:37.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}It's over.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:47.35,1:14:49.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天啊\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Oh, God!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:20.09,1:15:21.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有动静\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}We got some movement.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:22.02,1:15:25.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-两个人 -是谁？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- Who? Who is it? - Two of'em. Eagles 11 and 12.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:25.22,1:15:27.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-11、12号，古斯比和梅森 -我就知道\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- I-It's Goodspeed and Mason. - I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:28.06,1:15:31.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们得尽快另外让别人组成第二队， 展开第二次的行动\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I've gotta get a team together right now. We've gotta move with the second option.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:31.26,1:15:33.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让他们再被屠杀？不行\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}What, and invite another massacre? No way.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:33.47,1:15:37.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里只剩一只老狐狸和菜鸟，我告诉你，他们这儿没戏唱了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}We've got a 60-year-old convict and a lab rat. I'm telling you, it's over.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:37.60,1:15:40.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅森还没玩完，不是吗？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Not for Mason, it isn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:51.65,1:15:55.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,古斯比，我不会杀你的\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Goodspeed, I'm not gonna kill you.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:58.39,1:16:00.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你上哪儿？ -离开此地\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- Where are you going? - Off this bloody island.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:01.16,1:16:03.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}What? Wh-Wh-What for?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:03.30,1:16:06.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,古斯比？古斯比，你收到吗？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Goodspeed. Goodspeed, do you read me?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:07.00,1:16:09.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找你的\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}It's for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:10.90,1:16:13.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-长官？ -情况如何？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- Sir? - What's the status?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:13.47,1:16:15.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们全死了，死了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}The status is they're dead. They're dead!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:16.11,1:16:18.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只剩我和梅森，梅森正要走\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}It's just me and Mason. Now he says he's leaving.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:18.44,1:16:21.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行，听到吗？不行！\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}That is unacceptable. Do you hear me? Unacceptable!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:21.95,1:16:25.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有点麻烦，长官，他手上有枪\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Well, there's a problem, sir. He's got a gun.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:25.35,1:16:27.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你只有水枪吗？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}What do you have, a fuckin' water pistol?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:27.39,1:16:31.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-不是 -去阻止他\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- No, sir. - Go after him and stop him.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:33.36,1:16:35.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我并不想这样\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I didn't want this.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:35.70,1:16:38.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-天啊，我并不想这样 -这是无可避免的，法兰克\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- Jesus, I didn't want this. - You knew this might happen, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:38.50,1:16:41.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许他们会付钱给我们，也许不会\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- Well, maybe now they'll pay up. - Maybe now they won't, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:41.70,1:16:44.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许我们该处决一些人质\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Then maybe we need to execute a few hostages.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:44.34,1:16:46.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-有一个活口 -打死他\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- Got a live one! - Put a bullet in him.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:47.14,1:16:49.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你听到了，解决他\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You heard him. End it!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:49.18,1:16:51.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,收起手枪\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Holster that sidearm, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:09.66,1:17:11.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,长官\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Sir?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:15.03,1:17:19.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你犯了大错,害他们白白牺牲\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You made a terrible mistake.And more of our brothers have died in vain.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:20.04,1:17:23.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你们逼我的\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Damn you for forcing me into this position.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:27.15,1:17:30.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我现在就要单独跟你谈谈\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I need to talk to you right now, alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:30.18,1:17:32.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说这是最高机密\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Now you told me I'm on a need-to-know basis.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:32.59,1:17:34.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我现在告诉你\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}And I'm tellin' you right now, I need to know...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:34.89,1:17:38.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要知道约翰・梅森的身份，长官\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}who the fuck John Mason is right now, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:38.26,1:17:42.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真的想知道？一九六二年\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}All right, you wanna know? 1962, J. Edgar Hoover...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:42.30,1:17:44.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡佛掌管调查局,有人说他控管了整个国家\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}is head of the FBI, some say the country.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:45.16,1:17:49.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他秘密调查美国和欧洲的政要\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}It's no secret he kept microfilm files on prominent Americans and Europeans:
Dialogue: 0,1:17:49.20,1:17:52.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戴高乐、英国议员和首相\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}de Gaulle, British members of Parliament, even the prime minister.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:52.81,1:17:56.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他有每个人的秘密档案\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I mean, this guy had dirt on everybody in the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:56.18,1:17:59.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我听过传闻，这和梅森又有何关系？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Yeah, I know all the cloak-and-dagger stories. Where does Mason fit in?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:59.78,1:18:02.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是偷走档案的英国间谍\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Mason was the British operative who stole the files.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:02.62,1:18:05.28,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我们在加拿大边界逮到他\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}But our Bureau agents caught him at the Canadian border.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:05.45,1:18:08.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然英国说"从未听说过这个人"...\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Of course, the British claimed they'd never heard of him.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:08.75,1:18:13.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们将他囚禁，逼他交出胶片\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}And we held him without trial until he gave up the microfilm,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:13.36,1:18:15.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是他没有交出来\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}but he never did.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:15.43,1:18:18.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真令人讶异，胡佛没用他女儿逼他\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Well, I'm surprised Hoover didn't use his daughter as leverage.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:18.76,1:18:21.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡佛于一九七二年去世，那时她还没出世\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Hoover was dead in '72. She wasn't born yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:21.77,1:18:25.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在的调查局不同了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Today, well, it's a different Bureau.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:25.34,1:18:29.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他被关了一辈子，没有任何公平的审判 也难怪他会生气\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}So you held this guy without trial his whole life! No wonder he's pissed.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:29.68,1:18:33.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个人知道美国近半世纪以来的秘密\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}This man knows our most intimate secrets from the last half century:
Dialogue: 0,1:18:34.15,1:18:38.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外星人登陆，杀肯尼迪的真凶\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}the alien landing at Roswell, the truth about the J.F.K. assassination.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:39.12,1:18:42.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅森很生气 梅森很危险，他是个职业杀手\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}And Mason's angry, he's lethal, he's a trained killer.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:43.12,1:18:47.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而他也是我们手上唯一的希望\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}And he is the only hope that we have got.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:48.26,1:18:52.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅森 梅森\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Mason! Mason!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:52.60,1:18:55.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上面有81名人质\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}There are 81 hostages still up there.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:55.77,1:18:57.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，我也是人质\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Yeah, like me.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:57.67,1:19:00.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想来硬的？ 你想跟我来硬的？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}All right, you wanna play tough? You wanna play tough with me?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:00.37,1:19:03.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，FBI！ 别动，浑蛋\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Okay. FBI! Freeze, sucker!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:04.51,1:19:08.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我会开枪的 -不，你不会\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- I'll fire. - No, you won't.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:08.71,1:19:13.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-放下枪 -你不是那种人\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- Throw down. - You're not the sort.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:13.29,1:19:15.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们等着瞧吧\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Let's find out.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:18.69,1:19:21.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是，你不是\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I could; you, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:21.46,1:19:24.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且保险栓没除下\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Besides, your safety's on.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:24.83,1:19:28.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,古斯比，你的情况解决了吗？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Goodspeed, have you resolved the situation?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:28.50,1:19:31.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还没有\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:32.00,1:19:37.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在枪都在他手上了，该死！\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}-He's got all the guns now, sir. -Shit!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:37.31,1:19:40.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错，我不用枪，我也不会踹门\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You're right, I don't use guns and I don't kick down doors.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:40.51,1:19:42.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-这才是我在做的事 -我没戴眼镜\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- This is what I do. - I haven't got my glasses.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:42.85,1:19:47.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上面写：化学武器专家\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}What it says is Chemical Weapons Specialist.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:47.19,1:19:48.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:48.75,1:19:51.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那疯子有十五枚\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I got a lunatic up there, man with 15 missiles...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:52.02,1:19:53.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,致命的毒气导弹在上面\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}armed with some really funky stuff.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:54.06,1:19:59.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沃马克这大骗子 你可以警告我女儿的\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}That lying Womack. You could've told my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:59.77,1:20:04.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是机密 我也面临相同的状况\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}It was classified. Look, I'm in the same situation.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.40,1:20:07.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怀孕的女友也在旧金山\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}They've got my girlfriend in the city with a baby on the way.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:07.71,1:20:11.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能拆除导弹，我真的可以\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Look, I can defuse the rockets. I really can.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:11.28,1:20:14.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过我现在需要你的帮忙\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}But I'm gonna need your help, and I'm gonna need it right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:22.56,1:20:25.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,长官，他的武器和通话机不见了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Sir, this man's weapons and tack radio are missing!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:25.42,1:20:28.45,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该死 有鼠辈横行，把他们揪出来\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Shit, we got a rodent problem. Flush the pipes.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:28.63,1:20:31.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,底下的隧道像迷宫\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}There's probably a maze of tunnels on this goddamn island.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:31.36,1:20:33.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仔细搜\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- Check every access you can find. - Sir!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:39.77,1:20:42.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算你逃出恶魔岛\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Even if you escape from the island...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:42.34,1:20:45.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也躲不过导弹的\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}you can't escape the rockets.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:45.31,1:20:47.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你打算逃到哪儿？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}So, where are you gonna go?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:47.75,1:20:50.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要到哪里？你打算做什么？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Go where? What are, what are you gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:53.25,1:20:55.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我停尸间在哪儿？梅森\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Show me where the morgue is, Mason.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:55.59,1:20:57.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要出去了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I'm out of here.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:59.93,1:21:02.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不管你的女儿吗？梅森？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}What about your daughter? Mason?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:04.96,1:21:06.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到鼠辈\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Rodents located.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:06.53,1:21:10.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看你别无选择，对吧？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}The way I see it, you don't really have any choice, do you?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:10.70,1:21:12.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不认为你有\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I don't think you do.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:24.35,1:21:28.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快跑！\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Move!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:51.88,1:21:55.81,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-他们盯上我们了 -用火把他们烧出来\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- They're onto us. - Burn 'em out.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:58.05,1:22:00.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这玩意可厉害了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}This mother's gonna blow big.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:41.43,1:22:45.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不了解，怎么会突然失去通讯？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I don't understand. How could we lose radio contact all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:45.60,1:22:48.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们失去通讯了，但雷达还有显示\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}We've lost coms. Still got 'em on locaters.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:56.04,1:22:59.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你怎么说？ -什么？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- So what's it gonna be? - What?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:59.45,1:23:03.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你有别的选择吗？ -没有\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- How do you like your choices? - I don't.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:03.92,1:23:07.51,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就这么说\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}That's what I thought.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:07.69,1:23:09.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来吧\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}All right, come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:09.69,1:23:12.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是恶魔岛最古老的地方\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}This is the oldest part of Alcatraz.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:12.56,1:23:16.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这原来是美国内战的碉堡\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Did you know it was originally a Civil War fort?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:16.26,1:23:19.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？你知道吗，我也喜欢历史\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Oh, really? Huh. Yeah, wow. You know, I like history, too...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:19.37,1:23:22.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许这一切结束后，咱们再来研究\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}and maybe when this is all over, you and I can stop by the souvenir shop together.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:22.60,1:23:26.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过现在我只想找到导弹\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}But right now I just-- I just-- I wanna find some rockets.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:27.07,1:23:30.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别惹火我\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Don't tempt me.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:30.21,1:23:33.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们正要去停尸间\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}We are going to the morgue.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:55.77,1:23:59.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你可以吗？ -我会尽力而为\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- You sure you're ready for this? - I'll do my best.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:59.21,1:24:01.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你会尽力而为？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Your best?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:01.81,1:24:05.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,输家总是抱怨他们已经尽力了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Losers always whine about their best.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:05.31,1:24:09.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赢家才能搞上选美皇后\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Winners go home and fuck the prom queen.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:10.78,1:24:12.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡拉是选美皇后\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Carla was the prom queen.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:12.79,1:24:16.31,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-真的吗？ -真的\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- Really? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:18.06,1:24:20.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷达显示他们接近停尸间\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Locaters have them approaching the morgue, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:20.99,1:24:23.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油，你办得到的\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Come on, come on. You can do it, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:31.40,1:24:33.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,千万别迟疑\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You must never hesitate.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:57.00,1:24:59.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你差点射到导弹\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I think you're shooting too close to the rocket.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:59.93,1:25:02.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别射到导弹\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Him, but not the rocket.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:02.33,1:25:04.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有什么吩咐吗？教授\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Any other news, Professor?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:06.54,1:25:10.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别射到导弹！别射到导弹！\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Not the rocket! Not the rocket.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:24.42,1:25:26.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要让你们好看\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I got a little somethin' for ya.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:50.18,1:25:54.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我见过死的最惨的人\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Oh, yeah, okay. That's just about the most awful thing I've ever seen.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:56.06,1:26:02.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅森...一不小心，你就会送命\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Mason...the second you don't respect this, it kills you.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:02.39,1:26:04.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放过去\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Put it over there.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:15.41,1:26:18.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看过尸体，那样算是正常的吗？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You've been around a lot of corpses. Is that normal?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:18.38,1:26:21.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 脚在抖？ - 对，就是脚在抖\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- What, the feet thing? - Yeah, the feet thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:21.71,1:26:26.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-那很正常 -那让我不能专心，你可以想点办法吗？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- Yeah, that happens. - Can you do something about it?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:26.32,1:26:28.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要怎样？再杀死他一次吗？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Well, like what?  Kill him again?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:29.09,1:26:31.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听着，我只是个生化专家\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Listen, I'm just a biochemist.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:31.59,1:26:35.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成天关在实验室，生活平淡\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}And most of the time I work in a glass jar and lead a very uneventful life.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:35.99,1:26:39.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开着棕色的富豪车\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I drive a Volvo, a beige one. But what I'm dealing with here...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:39.87,1:26:43.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过我现在要处理的是这世上最致命的物质\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}is one of the most deadly substances the Earth has ever known.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:43.60,1:26:45.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以拜托你别惹我\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}So what do you say you cut me some friggin' slack?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:02.29,1:27:04.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一串串相当晶莹剔透\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}A really elegant string-of-pearls configuration.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:04.36,1:27:07.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是很不幸的是，它们非常不稳定\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Unfortunately, incredibly unstable.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:07.23,1:27:09.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这东西能有什么作用？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Well, what exactly does this stuff do?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:09.43,1:27:13.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果导弹将之汽化，能够杀死一个城市的居民\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}If the rocket renders it aerosol, it can take out the entire city of people.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:13.63,1:27:17.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？如果你掉下一个呢？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Really? And what happens if you drop one?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:18.07,1:27:20.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幸运的话，只杀死我们俩\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Happily, it'll just wipe out you and me.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:21.14,1:27:24.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么杀法？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- How? - It's a cholinesterase inhibitor.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:24.54,1:27:27.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它在三十秒之内会切断大脑至脊椎的神经信息\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}It stops the brain from sending nerve messages down the spinal cord within 30 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:27.95,1:27:30.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你暴露在它之下，你就会懂了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Any epidermal exposure or inhalation, and you'll know.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:31.12,1:27:35.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毒药侵袭神经系统，导致后背部剧痛\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}A twinge at the small of your back as the poison seizes your nervous system.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:35.92,1:27:37.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别动它\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Do not move that!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:40.06,1:27:43.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的肌肉收缩、呼吸困难\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Your muscles freeze, you can't breathe.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:43.26,1:27:46.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,强烈的痉挛，能让你翻搅出五腑内脏\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You spasm so hard you break your own back, spit your guts out.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:46.40,1:27:51.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-不过皮肤会先融化 -我的天啊\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- But that's after your skin melts off. - My God.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:52.00,1:27:55.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想我们希望现在老天是站在我们这边的，对吧\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Oh, I think we'd like God on our side at the moment, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:55.41,1:27:59.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我现在要把导航晶片拆掉\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}So what I'm doing now is removing the guidance system chips...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:59.85,1:28:03.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,导弹在五百尺后会落海\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}so the rocket will splash down after 500 feet.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:03.32,1:28:06.28,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给我 你可以放手\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}All right, let me have that. You can let go of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:06.45,1:28:09.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,退后、退后\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}All right, just back away. Just back away!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:09.22,1:28:12.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,长官，停尸间小队没有回音\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Sir, morgue team has not checked in.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:15.06,1:28:17.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,黑鸟一号，这是黑鸟，请回答\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Blackbird One, this is Blackbird. Over.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:17.30,1:28:22.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,黑鸟一号，这是黑鸟，请回答，该死的\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Blackbird One, this is Blackbird. Come in, goddamn it!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:24.27,1:28:27.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有敌人，快去\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Somebody's still there. Let's move!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:27.94,1:28:30.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有鼠辈，封锁停尸间，封锁停尸间\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Rats alive! Close on the morgue. Close on the morgue.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:30.34,1:28:32.28,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快，快，快\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Go, go, go, go, go, go, go.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:32.44,1:28:35.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,动作快点，我们还有敌人\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Frye, Darrow, hustle up. We got more company!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:39.42,1:28:44.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到停尸间会合，快去\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Hold it. Converge on the morgue. Move out.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:44.26,1:28:47.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,古斯比，快过来\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Goodspeed, come on. Come over here.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:47.69,1:28:51.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我最爱压力了，那是我每天的家常便饭\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Good. I love pressure. I eat it for breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:51.30,1:28:52.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点，来不及了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Come on. Time's up.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:53.03,1:28:56.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有三枚导弹在别的地方，我们一定要找到它们\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}There's three rockets somewhere else. We have to find them.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:58.67,1:28:59.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:23.13,1:29:26.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我玩这个太老了 -这会到哪儿？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- I'm too old for this. - Where's it go?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:26.67,1:29:28.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不晓得\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I've no idea.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:28.93,1:29:31.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,长官，所有的导航晶片都不见了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Sir, all the guidance chips are gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:31.64,1:29:34.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没除掉鼠辈\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Captain, I guess you didn't quite take care of the rat problem.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:34.74,1:29:36.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，长官\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}No, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:36.28,1:29:39.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里死了两个人，建议你最好把他们解决掉\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Well, there are two dead men here who strongly suggest you go finish the job.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:39.28,1:29:41.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，长官!是的，长官！\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Yes, sir. Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:50.16,1:29:53.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你不晓得通往哪儿？ -没错，我不知道\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}-You really don't know where this goes? -No, I don't know where it goes.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:53.89,1:29:57.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们速度越来越快了，你知道怎么让它慢下来吗\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Well, it's starting to pick up speed. Do you know how to slow it down?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:57.30,1:29:58.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，我不知道\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}No, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:34.27,1:30:38.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅森，你还好吧？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Mason, you all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:38.60,1:30:42.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好得很，你这个大白痴\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Yes, perfectly okay, you fucking idiot!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:44.08,1:30:46.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们追来了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}They're coming.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:46.24,1:30:48.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-谁？ -海军陆战队\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- Who? - The marines!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:48.91,1:30:49.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪里？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Where?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:52.08,1:31:55.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-怎么回事？ -把他拦住\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- What the fuck's goin' on? - Let's cut him off.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:18.77,1:32:19.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅森\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Mason!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:23.58,1:32:25.81,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅森\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Mason!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:41.09,1:33:46.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这浑蛋！去死吧！死吧！死吧！\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You motherfucker! Die! Die! Die!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:07.05,1:34:10.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很高兴你没有考虑太久\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I'm rather glad you didn't hesitate too long.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:13.52,1:34:17.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么能保持冷静？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}How do you do it?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:17.59,1:34:23.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我受过世界顶尖的英国情报局严格训练\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Oh, I was trained by the best. British lntelligence.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:23.36,1:34:26.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来吧\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:26.33,1:34:31.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老实说，我情愿当诗人或农夫\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}But in retrospect, I'd rather have been a poet or a farmer.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:33.89,1:34:37.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,<font size=20 color=#00d8f8>时限：8小时
Dialogue: 0,1:34:37.61,1:34:40.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总统三小时后到\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Okay, the president arrives in three hours.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:41.05,1:34:45.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能拖多久就拖，然后进行空袭\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}His directive is to string Hummel along until the air strike is operational.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:45.35,1:34:47.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,铝热剂进展如何？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}What's the word from Mohave, General?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:47.55,1:34:52.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是一样，他们正在赶工\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}The same as last time, Lou. They're going as fast as they can.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:56.63,1:35:00.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跪下来\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Do it over here. On your knees. On your knees!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:10.94,1:35:14.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特遣队员，你手上有我的东西\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Navy SEALs, listen up. You've got something that belongs to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:14.35,1:35:16.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正确的说是十二片导航晶片\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Twelve guidance chips, to be precise.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:16.88,1:35:21.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我提醒你们，我手上有危在旦夕的人质\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Let me remind you there are lives at stake, civilian lives.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:21.62,1:35:23.28,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说话\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Speak up.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:23.46,1:35:26.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-说话！-我…嗯…\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- Speak up! - I, uh, uh--
Dialogue: 0,1:35:26.49,1:35:28.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉他们你的名字\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Tell them your name.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:28.49,1:35:30.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫赖瑞・韩德逊\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}My name is Larry Henderson.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:30.76,1:35:32.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Oh, man.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:32.56,1:35:35.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有三个孩子\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}And I'm a father of three.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:35.50,1:35:38.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他拿枪指着我的脑袋\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}they've got a gun to my head.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:38.40,1:35:42.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们有三分钟可以交出导航晶片\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You've got exactly three minutes to return the guidance chips
Dialogue: 0,1:35:42.27,1:35:44.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,否则韩德逊先生就没命了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}or Mr. Henderson won't have a head.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:45.08,1:35:47.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噢…不\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Oh, no. Hey. What--?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:47.95,1:35:53.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有三枚导弹，你去找，并且拆除它们\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Now, three to go. You find them and defuse them,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:53.92,1:35:57.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-好吗？ -好的\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- okay?All right. - All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:57.96,1:36:01.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去找汉默，试着帮你拖延一些时间\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I'll try and delay Hummel and give you more time.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:01.39,1:36:04.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那韩德逊的脑袋呢？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Hey, what about Mr. Henderson's head?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:06.77,1:36:09.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没问题？什么意思？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Okay? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:14.64,1:36:16.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:29.32,1:36:32.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-将军 -你是什么人\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- General. - Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:34.69,1:36:36.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就是剩下来的敌人\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I'm all that's left of the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:51.14,1:36:52.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Bingo.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:01.59,1:37:03.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把手放下\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Stand easy.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:06.22,1:37:10.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为自己是老兵\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Thought I'd been in the service a long time.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:10.73,1:37:14.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-姓名和军阶，水手？ -事实上，我是陆军\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- Name and rank, sailor. - Well, it's army, actually.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:15.03,1:37:19.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回答问题，并且尊称他为“将军”\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Answer the question. And address him as "General, sir."
Dialogue: 0,1:37:20.47,1:37:23.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,约翰・梅森上尉，将军\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Captain John Patrick Mason, General, sir...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:23.74,1:37:25.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隶属于皇家特种部队\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}of Her Majesty's S.A.S.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:25.94,1:37:27.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然，已经退伍了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Retired, of course.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:31.55,1:37:34.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你离家稍微远了点，上尉\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You're a long way from home, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:34.39,1:37:36.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎么与此事牵扯上的？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}How the hell are you involved in this?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:37.16,1:37:39.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我对这座监狱相当熟悉\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Oh, I have a unique knowledge of this prison facility.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:39.89,1:37:42.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以前曾在这里作过客\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I was, uh, formerly a guest here.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:56.81,1:37:59.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨，小家伙\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Hi, sweetie.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:06.12,1:38:08.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给我回来，小男孩\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Hey, come back here, little boy.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:10.52,1:38:13.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们有告诉你我的目的\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Did they bother to tell you who I am, why I'm doing this?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:13.53,1:38:16.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是只是利用你而已？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Or are they just using you like they do everybody else?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:16.63,1:38:20.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只知道电视上说你是个越战英雄\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}All I know is you were big in Vietnam. I saw the highlights on television.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:20.53,1:38:24.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你根本就不知道\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You wouldn't have any fucking idea what it means to lead some of the finest men on God's earth into battle,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:24.34,1:38:26.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到优秀军人被他们的政府出卖的痛苦\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}and then see their memory betrayed by their own fuckin' government.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:26.70,1:38:31.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看不出屠杀一百万人如何能安慰他们的英灵？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I don't quite see how you cherish the memory of the dead by killing another million.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:31.68,1:38:35.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且…这不是战争\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}And, uh, this is not combat.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:35.61,1:38:39.81,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是疯狂行径，将军\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}It's an act of lunacy, General, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:39.98,1:38:42.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我认为是个大白痴\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Personally, I think you're a fuckin' idiot.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:48.96,1:38:51.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“自由之树必须以爱国者和暴君的血灌溉开花”\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}"The tree of liberty must be refreshed from time to time...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:51.70,1:38:54.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,汤玛士・杰斐逊说的\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}with the blood of patriots and tyrants." Thomas Jefferson.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:55.10,1:38:59.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,王尔德说过“爱国主义是邪恶的美德”\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}"Patriotism is the virtue of the vicious," according to Oscar Wilde.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:04.88,1:39:06.81,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你证明我的观点\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Thank you for making my point.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:06.98,1:39:11.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,导航晶片呢？导航晶片呢？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Where are the guidance chips? Where are the guidance chips?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:11.42,1:39:13.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我毁掉了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I destroyed them.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:13.75,1:39:15.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不该这么做的\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}That was a bad move, soldier.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:15.72,1:39:18.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你要处决我们吗？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Does that mean you'll execute us both?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:46.55,1:39:50.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算你走运，汉默要抓活的\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You're lucky that old man Hummel wants you alive.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:50.22,1:39:52.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我倒很乐意把你开膛剖肚\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}'Cause I'll take pleasure in guttin' you, boy.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:55.10,1:39:59.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,<font size=20 color=#00d8f8>时限：52分钟
Dialogue: 0,1:39:59.36,1:40:04.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我倒很乐意把你开膛剖肚\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I'd take pleasure in guttin' you...boy!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:04.37,1:40:09.81,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我倒很乐意把你开膛剖肚\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}"I'll take pleasure in guttin' you, boy."
Dialogue: 0,1:40:09.94,1:40:11.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些人是怎么了？梅森\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}What is wrong with these people, huh, Mason?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:11.91,1:40:15.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这岛上到处都充满了愤怒\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Don't you think there's a lot of,uh,a lot of anger floating around this island?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:16.11,1:40:19.28,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一大堆莽撞青少年\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Kind of a pubescent volatility? Don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:19.45,1:40:23.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不认为他们满怀苦恼 心中都充满了杀父情结\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}A lot of angst, a lot of, "I'm 16, I'm angry at my father" syndrome?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:23.76,1:40:26.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成熟点吧！\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I mean, grow up! We're stuck on an island...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:26.19,1:40:29.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们跟一群噬血如命的变态军人混在一起\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}with a bunch of violence-for-pleasure seeking psychopathic marines.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:29.23,1:40:31.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们真丢脸\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Shame on them!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:34.30,1:40:37.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只拆除了一枚导弹，还剩两枚没拆\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Anyway, I only got one chem round. There's two left.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:37.64,1:40:39.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅森？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Mason?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:39.30,1:40:41.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在这儿\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Yes, I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:41.74,1:40:44.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真怀念\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I was just thinking how wonderful it was...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:44.51,1:40:46.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当时不准说话的日子\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}when the inmates weren't allowed to talk in here.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:47.11,1:40:49.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不准说话？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Not allowed to talk.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:49.91,1:40:51.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么受的了？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}How did you do it?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:52.12,1:40:56.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在心里满怀希望\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Uh, nurtured the hope that there was hope.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:56.96,1:41:00.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望有一天能重获自由\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}That one day I'd breathe free air.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:00.56,1:41:03.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许还能见到我的女儿\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Perhaps meet my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:04.00,1:41:08.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望很卑微，却能让人保持求生意志\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Modest hopes, but, uh, they kept a man alive.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:08.60,1:41:11.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么会被关起来？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}What'd they put you away for, John?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:11.80,1:41:14.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说来话长\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Oh, that's a long story.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:14.57,1:41:17.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正我哪里也去不成\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Well, I'm not goin' anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:17.21,1:41:20.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的人有多久没有回音了？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}When was the last communication from our men on Alcatraz?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:20.95,1:41:23.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,七个小时\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Seven hours.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:25.65,1:41:28.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-铝热剂完成了 -帮我接总统\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- Thermite plasma is operational. - Get me the president.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:29.05,1:41:33.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请坐，请各位保持随时待命\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Be seated.Gentlemen, consider yourselveson ground alert.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:33.76,1:41:36.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一旦出发，你们的任务\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}If we receive launch authority. your mission is...
Dialogue: 0,1:41:36.33,1:41:38.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是彻底摧毁恶魔岛\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}the complete thermal destruction of Alcatraz lsland.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:38.76,1:41:42.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每一寸地都必须完全摧毁，不能有任何漏失\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}The entire island is to be blanketed, not one square inch missed.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:43.03,1:41:48.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,81名平民以及部份军人将会在这次攻击中牺牲\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Eighty-one American civilians and a number of U.S. Marines will lose their lives in this air strike.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:50.01,1:41:55.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你何不交出胶片以解决问题呢？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Why didn't you just tell them where the microfilm was and create a solution?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:55.41,1:42:00.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一旦胶片拿到手，他们就会让我死\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Hmph. The moment they had the microfilm, they'd suicide me.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:00.49,1:42:03.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-这是他们的解决办法 -结果你被关在这儿\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- Some solution. - And you ended up here.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:03.72,1:42:07.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这让我想到另一个问题\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Which brings me to another question.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:07.29,1:42:10.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当年你逃狱的时候…我干脆直讲吧\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}When you broke out--Let me see if I can get this straight.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:10.86,1:42:14.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你当年下到焚化炉的滑运道，坐上矿坑小车\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You went down the incinerator chute.on the mine cars,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:14.97,1:42:17.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,穿过隧道到达发电厂\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}through the tunnels to the power plant.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:18.07,1:42:21.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后再穿过蒸气引擎，那招真的很帅\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}under the steam engine-- That was really cool, by the way--
Dialogue: 0,1:42:21.57,1:42:24.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,进入贮水池，然后从水管逃出去\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}and into the cistern through the intake pipe.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:24.88,1:42:29.51,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过你到底\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}But how, in the name of Zeus's butthole...
Dialogue: 0,1:42:29.68,1:42:31.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是怎么逃出囚房的？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}did you get out of your cell?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:31.78,1:42:35.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我之所以问的原因，是因为就我们目前的处境\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I only ask because in our current situation...
Dialogue: 0,1:42:35.42,1:42:41.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这招应该会…很有用！\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}well, it could prove to be useful information, maybe!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:58.98,1:43:01.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,专业秘密，孩子\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Trade secrets, my son.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:05.18,1:43:07.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将军，我们只剩两枚可用的导弹\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}General, two operational rockets left.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:07.72,1:43:10.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一枚在灯塔，一枚在屋顶\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}One's at the lower lighthouse and there is one on the roof.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:10.19,1:43:14.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,两枚都随时待命了，长官 将军，你听到吗？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}And both of the birds are ready to fly, sir.General, can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:14.36,1:43:17.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我听到了，上尉 - 我只想确定一下\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- I heard you, Captain. - Oh, just makin' sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:19.10,1:43:22.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们是否该准备发射了？将军\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Should we prepare for launch, General?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:23.37,1:43:27.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我来决定战略，上尉 -我懂了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- I'll handle the strategy, Captain. - Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:27.54,1:43:32.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,时间快到了 我只想让你知道这点,长官\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}The hour is approaching, sir.Just letting the General know of the time, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:32.71,1:43:34.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这点我很清楚，上尉\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I'm very aware of the time, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:34.75,1:43:36.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，长官,只是要让你知道\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Aye, aye, sir. Lettin' you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:37.15,1:43:39.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和我的弟兄都准备好了,准备好好大干一场\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Me and my boys are ready to cock, lock, and ready to rock.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:42.12,1:43:44.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅森，你要上哪儿去？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Mason, where're you going?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:44.36,1:43:47.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三十年前，我就发誓,我决不能死在这里\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Thirty years ago I vowed I wouldn't die in this toilet.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:47.36,1:43:51.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不能走 那里有个狂人的手里正操纵着导弹的发射按钮\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You're not leaving! There's a madman in there with his hand on a, on a button!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:51.83,1:43:55.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他会被狙击手一枪打死的\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Shh. Some sniper's gonna get his ass.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:55.70,1:43:58.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,站住，梅森\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Stop moving, Mason.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:59.84,1:44:02.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅森，别动\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Mason, stop moving.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:02.47,1:44:05.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,汉默不会下手的 他是个军人,不是个谋杀犯\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Hummel won't do it. He's a soldier, not a murderer.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:05.81,1:44:07.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我从他的眼神看得出来\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I read it in his eyes.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:08.15,1:44:11.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你从他的眼神看得出来？那敢情好！\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You read his eyes?Oh, well, then everything's just fine!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:11.92,1:44:15.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-但我不能冒这个险 -拜托你再大声点\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- I can't afford to take that chance. - Why don't you talk louder?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:15.22,1:44:17.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还剩三分钟\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Three minutes to go, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:19.56,1:44:22.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们不会打电话来了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- They're not gonna call, Frank. - Oh, they'll call.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:22.56,1:44:25.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我们发射一枚导弹,他们就会打电话来的\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}They'll call if we fire one of our rockets up their ass.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:33.70,1:44:36.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我是汉默 -法兰克，我是克拉玛\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- Hummel. - Hi, Frank. It's AI Kramer here.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:36.57,1:44:39.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-怎么样了？ -你认为呢？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- How's it going out there? - How do you think it's going?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:39.51,1:44:43.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-听着，我们还需要一小时 -你们只剩三分钟\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- Listen, on this end we're gonna need another hour, Frank. - You've got three minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:43.28,1:44:47.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-法兰克,我们得等总统… -你们只有三分钟\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- Listen, uh, Frank, we have to get final authorization from the president. - You've got three minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:47.52,1:44:50.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,法兰克，请你别做出傻事\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Frank, please don't do anything stupid.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:51.09,1:44:54.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们还需要一个小时\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}They want another hour.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:54.93,1:44:58.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鬼扯 他们在骗人，将军\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Well, that's bullshit. That's bullshit, General. They're lyin'!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:58.40,1:45:02.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们在耍你，把你当白痴,长官\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}They're calling our bluff, sir. They're playing you for a fool, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:02.60,1:45:07.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下令发射导弹，将军\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Order the launch, General.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:07.81,1:45:11.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点，将军 我们下定决心吧！\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Come on, General. Let's be all we can be.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:25.76,1:45:27.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,任务还没完成\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}The mission's not complete!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:27.99,1:45:29.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的任务完成了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Well, mine is.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:30.03,1:45:32.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个任务结束之后,你会回家\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}When this is over, you'll go back home...
Dialogue: 0,1:45:32.86,1:45:37.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开着你的棕色富豪轿车，载着卡拉和小宝宝兜风\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}driving Carla and your baby insane in your beige Volvo.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:37.70,1:45:41.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是死了就是回到监狱，那都没什么两样\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}And I'll be dead or back in prison, which is the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:41.37,1:45:45.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不能走\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You're not leaving.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:48.15,1:45:52.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 我自己来\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}All right, I'll do it myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:53.32,1:45:55.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我受过三星期武器训练\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I got three weeks' weapons training.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:55.59,1:45:59.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能消灭整排士兵\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I'll kick the-- Out of a platoon full of marines.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:00.02,1:46:02.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小意思\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}No problem.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:13.80,1:46:17.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少校，连接上屋顶的导弹\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- Major, patch me into Roof Battery. - Aye, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:17.17,1:46:21.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打开控制电路，准备接收目标方位\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Fire open control circuit coordinates to the roof, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:21.18,1:46:23.51,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:28.92,1:46:29.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-启动电源 -噢…不好\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- Laser powered up! - Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:32.82,1:46:35.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说，给我跪下\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I said, on your knees!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:35.76,1:46:38.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字叫史丹利・古斯比\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}My name's Stanley Goodspeed.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:38.40,1:46:41.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是FBI的化学武器专家\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I'm a chemical weapons specialist for the FBI.
