Dialogue: 0,1:47:16.17,1:47:19.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我上回游到对岸的时候，年龄才跟你差不多\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Hey, the last time I swam this channel I was your age.
