Dialogue: 0,1:49:59.93,1:50:03.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,导弹是怎么回事？座标怎么会变？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}What happened to the rocket? What the fuck happened?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:03.73,1:50:07.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎么回事？长官、少校！\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}What the fuck is going on to the coordinates? Sir! Major!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:07.20,1:50:09.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上尉，请你出去\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Captain, step outside.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:09.67,1:50:12.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 说话啊，长官 - 上尉，请你出去\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- Talk to me, sir. - Captain, step outside!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:25.86,1:50:27.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帮我接五角大厦\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Get me the Pentagon.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:40.94,1:50:43.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那算什么？法兰克\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}What the hell was that, Frank?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:45.18,1:50:48.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我说：那算… -我听到你说的了,就算你想犯上\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- I said, what the hell-- - I heard what you said! If you're gonna be insubordinate...
Dialogue: 0,1:50:48.61,1:50:51.51,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-也请你放尊重点 -废话少说，将军\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- I'd appreciate it if you'd do it with a little more respect. - Cut the crap, General.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:51.68,1:50:53.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你在做什么？ -我还不想伤害无辜百姓\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- What the hell are you doing? - I'm not ready to kill these people.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:54.05,1:50:56.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-打电话给五角大厦，再向他们争取时间 -不\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- Call the Pentagon. Ask for more time. - No!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:56.19,1:50:59.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点，法兰克，我们就快失控了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Do it, Frank! We're coming loose.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:59.36,1:51:02.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你才失控了，其他人还是很冷静的\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You're coming loose. The rest of us are in complete control.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:02.56,1:51:05.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我们要新的时限 - 放下电话\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- We're askin' 'em. We're askin' 'em for a new deadline. - Put the phone down.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:05.63,1:51:08.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 兄弟们开始失控了 - 他们是陆战队员\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- The men are falling apart. - The men are marines!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:08.27,1:51:12.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 是吗？ - 我找克拉玛将军\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Are they? I wanna talk to General Kramer.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:12.34,1:51:15.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我以老朋友的身份劝你 - 现在就打电话给他\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- You've been asked by an old friend. - Put him on the phone right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:15.14,1:51:17.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我以上司的身份命令你 -我是巴克斯特少校\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- You've been ordered by a superior officer. - This is Major Baxter.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:17.37,1:51:20.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以一个持枪者的身份 给你最后一次机会\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Now you're being given your last chance by a man with a gun.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:20.78,1:51:22.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把电话放下\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Put the phone down.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:25.52,1:51:29.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我以为你还没准备杀人 -我在开始准备了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- I thought you weren't ready to kill. - I'm warmin' up.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:29.95,1:51:32.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稍息\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}At ease.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:40.76,1:51:43.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你得做出决定，总统先生\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}They need a decision, Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:49.81,1:51:53.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过去这几个小时\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}These past few hours...
Dialogue: 0,1:51:53.81,1:51:58.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我生命中最漫长、最黑暗的时刻\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}have been the longest, darkest of my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:58.18,1:52:01.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人命该如何评估呢？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}How does one weigh human life?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:03.12,1:52:06.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一百万市民和81名人质\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}One million civilians against 81 hostages.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:06.69,1:52:09.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有法兰克汉默\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}And in the middle, Frank Hummel.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:10.13,1:52:14.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们忽视\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}That we have ignored,abandoned...
Dialogue: 0,1:52:14.50,1:52:18.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,并遗弃像汉默这样伟大的英雄\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}or marginalized a great soldier like Frank Hummel...
Dialogue: 0,1:52:18.97,1:52:22.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有那些被忽视，且为国捐驱的军人子弟\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}and that American boys have paid for that neglect...
Dialogue: 0,1:52:22.21,1:52:25.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同样地真实\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}in blood is equally real...
Dialogue: 0,1:52:25.71,1:52:28.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也同样地悲哀\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}and equally tragic.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:30.61,1:52:32.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们向恐怖行动宣战\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}We are at war with terror.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:32.88,1:52:36.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,战争必有伤亡\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Fighting a war means casualties.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:36.55,1:52:39.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我所做过最困难的决定\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}This is the worst call I've ever had to make.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:44.16,1:52:47.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,批准空袭行动\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Air strike approved.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:49.93,1:52:51.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,红雷，待命准备起飞\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Red Thunder to tower. Request clearance.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:52.04,1:52:55.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 投下这么多的弹药\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}With the amount of firepower they're gonna drop in there...
Dialogue: 0,1:52:55.44,1:52:58.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 塔台，准备起飞… -几秒就会完全毁灭并结束了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- Tower this is Strike Leader. Prepared to go. - it'll be over in a few seconds.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:58.68,1:53:01.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十七分钟后抵达目标\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Flight time to drop point: 17 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:08.05,1:53:11.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起，将军 恕我无理\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Excuse me, General, sir, with all due respect to you,
Dialogue: 0,1:53:11.49,1:53:14.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你倒底在搞什么鬼？ -你更改了座标，是不是，将军？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- what the fuck is going on? - You changed the coordinates, didn't you, General?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:14.39,1:53:17.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-没错，上尉 -现在他们以为我们没种\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- That's affirmative, Captain. - So, now they think we're gutless?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:17.73,1:53:20.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们什么都没做到\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}The Feds? They think we won't actually do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:20.53,1:53:23.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们会海上与空中全力进攻\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}They're gonna come at us with everything they've got. Air and sea.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:23.43,1:53:25.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把我们炸的粉身碎骨\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}They're gonna bomb our ass back to the Stone Age.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:25.87,1:53:27.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们不晓得我们是故意错开目标的\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}They don't know we missed on purpose.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:27.97,1:53:33.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了.我们不是没种，而是无能.对吧？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Great. We're not gutless, we're incompetent. That right?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:33.34,1:53:36.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不喜欢你的口气，上尉\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I don't think I like your tone, Captain. We planned for this contingency.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:36.85,1:53:39.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,带导弹和四名人质一起撤退\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Load the V.X. into the choppers, take four hostages and evacuate.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:39.95,1:53:42.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会留下来承担一切后果\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}The consequences of our actions I'll face alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:42.29,1:53:45.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起，将军，他妈的钱呢？\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Excuse me, General, but what about the fucking money?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:45.59,1:53:47.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有钱，任务结束\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}There is no fucking money. Mission's over.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:48.16,1:53:49.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才怪呢\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Bullshit it's over.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:50.03,1:53:53.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在跟一位将军讲话，维持军纪\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You're talking to a General, soldier. Maintain discipline.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:53.70,1:53:58.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是军人，少校 在我们挟持人质之后，我们就成了佣兵\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I'm not a soldier, Major.The day we took hostages we became mercenaries.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:58.47,1:54:03.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而佣兵要的是钱,我要我的钱\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}And mercenaries get paid I want my fucking money!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:03.34,1:54:05.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这项任务全靠武力威胁\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs16}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}This mission was based on the threat of force.
